{
  "texts": [
    "The enhanced reach and availability of LLM-Chatbots in addressing adolescent health issues could be instrumental in addressing the rising concerns in this area.",
    "However, their current limitations in identifying and preventing misinformation necessitate cautious application, awaiting further development of their analytical capabilities.The applicability of LLMs may also extend to various medical specializations, though their strengths and shortcomings could vary.",
    "For instance, Rasmussen et al. (2023) found ChatGPT-3.5 to be less effective in addressing treatment and prevention queries for Spring Catarrh [39], while Lahat et al.",
    "( 2023) noted its subpar performance in gastrointestinal diagnostic queries [40].",
    "These differences in LLM performance may stem from the varying depths of available internet data on each topic."
  ]
}